{{Top|leg}}
The '''VA-13 Sweeper''' was a [[Starship/Legends|ship]] constructed by the [[Daedalus Gas Mines]] Corporation for use in radiocarbon harvesting, which involved dredging an ion-rich atmosphere for radioactive [[Carbon/Legends|carbon]] isotopes.

The Sweeper was a modified [[Snubfighter/Legends|snubfighter]]. It had a 10-[[Meter/Legends|meter]] long, 1-meter high, finely-toothed trough made of a special metal attached to the nose of the ship. The metal attracted and absorbed the isotopes, which could be rendered into a more usable form.

The Sweepers were first used on [[Genarius]] for the first successful [[Mining/Legends|mining]] operation there, the [[City/Legends|city]] of [[Friz Harammel]].

